1
00:00:02,887 --> 00:00:07,899
♪Do you know, our fingertips
are bound by one string♪

2
00:00:07,900 --> 00:00:12,499
♪Tied to an attachment
that blooms only to fade♪

3
00:00:12,500 --> 00:00:13,999
♪By your side once♪

4
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:17,074
♪I laughed with the world
wild and free♪

5
00:00:17,075 --> 00:00:21,049
♪Yet now there's no one
to carry the story on♪

6
00:00:21,050 --> 00:00:25,970
♪Do you know you are the one string
woven through my fate♪

7
00:00:25,987 --> 00:00:30,699
♪Coiled through the years,
where longing sharpens into pain's line♪

8
00:00:30,700 --> 00:00:35,261
♪If love is meant to fall
more wretched the fiercer its flight♪

9
00:00:35,262 --> 00:00:40,445
♪Yet I still came to answer your call♪

10
00:00:40,725 --> 00:00:43,086
=Shall We Dance=

11
00:00:43,087 --> 00:00:46,157
=Episode 20=

12
00:00:46,350 --> 00:00:47,470
Xiao Man.

13
00:00:48,860 --> 00:00:51,300
General Xiang and Lord He were murdered.

14
00:00:51,500 --> 00:00:53,180
Who do you think carried it out?

15
00:00:53,500 --> 00:00:55,220
And who is behind it?

16
00:00:56,820 --> 00:00:58,140
Xiao Man is not clever,

17
00:00:58,500 --> 00:00:59,980
but no matter what,

18
00:01:00,380 --> 00:01:01,620
I believe

19
00:01:02,060 --> 00:01:03,700
the truth

20
00:01:03,820 --> 00:01:05,300
will surface soon.

21
00:01:08,100 --> 00:01:09,220
Xiao Man.

22
00:01:09,540 --> 00:01:11,620
I remember you once told me

23
00:01:12,260 --> 00:01:14,060
to dance whenever I felt unhappy.

24
00:01:15,820 --> 00:01:16,940
No wonder.

25
00:01:17,660 --> 00:01:19,020
No wonder what?

26
00:01:19,860 --> 00:01:22,380
No wonder it has been so long
since I last danced.

27
00:01:23,140 --> 00:01:24,619
It feels as though

28
00:01:24,620 --> 00:01:26,060
I have forgotten every move.

29
00:01:27,460 --> 00:01:29,420
If only many things in life

30
00:01:30,060 --> 00:01:31,780
could fade away like that.

31
00:01:33,340 --> 00:01:35,139
Xiao Man was young back then,

32
00:01:35,140 --> 00:01:36,340
and did not understand.

33
00:01:36,940 --> 00:01:38,860
Only recently did I realize

34
00:01:38,940 --> 00:01:40,740
that joy does not come from dancing,

35
00:01:40,860 --> 00:01:43,180
but from the one
who makes you want to dance.

36
00:01:44,220 --> 00:01:45,900
Fate plays cruel tricks.

37
00:01:46,420 --> 00:01:47,659
Many things,

38
00:01:47,660 --> 00:01:48,900
many people,

39
00:01:50,220 --> 00:01:52,380
may have been wrong from the very start.

40
00:01:54,600 --> 00:01:55,720
So,

41
00:01:56,100 --> 00:01:57,059
that childish line

42
00:01:57,060 --> 00:01:58,780
about dancing away unhappiness,

43
00:01:59,980 --> 00:02:01,780
please forget it, Your Majesty.

44
00:02:02,100 --> 00:02:03,220
Your Majesty.

45
00:02:04,540 --> 00:02:06,920
There is unrest at the border.
Foreign forces are advancing.

46
00:02:09,275 --> 00:02:10,395
I understand.

47
00:02:13,700 --> 00:02:16,980
You are much calmer than I expected.

48
00:02:19,140 --> 00:02:20,260
Xiao Man.

49
00:02:21,300 --> 00:02:24,220
The day I both feared and awaited
has finally arrived.

50
00:02:25,620 --> 00:02:28,180
The day we break free has come as well.

51
00:02:28,700 --> 00:02:31,060
I no longer need to play the fool.

52
00:02:32,940 --> 00:02:34,060
Duanmu Zhi.

53
00:02:34,620 --> 00:02:37,379
Summon the Grand Princess
and all ministers

54
00:02:37,380 --> 00:02:38,379
to the Imperial Study.

55
00:02:38,380 --> 00:02:39,460
Yes.

56
00:02:40,740 --> 00:02:41,620
Xiao Man.

57
00:02:42,620 --> 00:02:44,300
Help me change.

58
00:02:46,620 --> 00:02:49,740
Your Majesty must not lead the campaign
in person. It is far too dangerous.

59
00:02:50,500 --> 00:02:54,739
Aunt, with General Xiang now dead,
there is no commanding general in the army.

60
00:02:54,740 --> 00:02:56,020
The troops are shaken.

61
00:02:56,140 --> 00:02:57,739
Only if I lead them myself

62
00:02:57,740 --> 00:02:59,500
can this rebellion be put down.

63
00:03:00,340 --> 00:03:01,860
Lead the campaign in person.

64
00:03:02,220 --> 00:03:03,340
Your Majesty.

65
00:03:04,220 --> 00:03:05,700
Once you mount the tiger,

66
00:03:05,780 --> 00:03:07,420
there is no easy way down.

67
00:03:08,020 --> 00:03:08,979
Your Majesty.

68
00:03:08,980 --> 00:03:11,459
Though leading the campaign yourself
carries real danger,

69
00:03:11,460 --> 00:03:14,060
if Your Majesty establishes
authority in the army this time,

70
00:03:14,340 --> 00:03:15,979
then in the court thereafter,

71
00:03:15,980 --> 00:03:19,380
no one will dare defy your will again.

72
00:03:20,540 --> 00:03:21,659
Your Majesty.

73
00:03:21,660 --> 00:03:23,299
Princess, please be at ease.

74
00:03:23,300 --> 00:03:25,540
I will accompany
His Majesty to the front

75
00:03:25,580 --> 00:03:27,260
and ensure his safety.

76
00:03:29,220 --> 00:03:30,595
But...

77
00:03:30,980 --> 00:03:32,980
I only want to look impressive.

78
00:03:33,380 --> 00:03:34,900
I do not actually want to fight.

79
00:03:39,900 --> 00:03:40,780
Sun Gong.

80
00:03:40,980 --> 00:03:42,500
This expedition beyond the frontier,

81
00:03:42,660 --> 00:03:44,100
I fear it may be dangerous.

82
00:03:45,060 --> 00:03:47,659
Your Majesty, as Minister of War,

83
00:03:47,660 --> 00:03:49,139
it is my duty to protect you.

84
00:03:49,140 --> 00:03:50,460
I will not shrink from it.

85
00:03:51,180 --> 00:03:52,540
Then it is settled.

86
00:03:52,900 --> 00:03:54,019
Minister Sun.

87
00:03:54,020 --> 00:03:57,460
Tomorrow we march together
to the frontier

88
00:03:57,780 --> 00:03:59,100
and bring this war to an end.

89
00:04:07,740 --> 00:04:09,180
This march to the frontier

90
00:04:09,220 --> 00:04:11,220
will you truly collude
with foreign forces,

91
00:04:11,500 --> 00:04:14,220
and bury Great Qian's elite troops
beyond the pass?

92
00:04:14,380 --> 00:04:15,500
Yes.

93
00:04:15,740 --> 00:04:18,340
Only by joining with them
can victory be assured.

94
00:04:20,460 --> 00:04:22,819
You and Mother
guarded the frontier for years.

95
00:04:22,820 --> 00:04:24,419
Can you truly bear to let the people

96
00:04:24,420 --> 00:04:26,739
Father and Mother
once protected with their lives

97
00:04:26,740 --> 00:04:28,660
suffer the horrors of war again?

98
00:04:29,540 --> 00:04:30,619
Enough.

99
00:04:30,620 --> 00:04:31,659
You stay in the Capital

100
00:04:31,660 --> 00:04:33,939
and carry out Uncle's next step.

101
00:04:33,940 --> 00:04:34,579
Then...

102
00:04:34,580 --> 00:04:35,620
Xiao Man.

103
00:04:35,900 --> 00:04:37,100
Ten years have passed.

104
00:04:37,140 --> 00:04:39,500
Do you remember
these carved likeness clearly?

105
00:04:39,940 --> 00:04:40,899
Father,

106
00:04:40,900 --> 00:04:41,980
Mother,

107
00:04:42,540 --> 00:04:45,580
Uncle in his youth,
and Brother as a boy,

108
00:04:46,620 --> 00:04:49,460
but not a single one of me.

109
00:04:50,980 --> 00:04:53,460
Mother never
had the chance to carve your likeness.

110
00:04:53,740 --> 00:04:55,140
That is precisely why

111
00:04:55,180 --> 00:04:57,140
you are the freest of all.

112
00:04:58,100 --> 00:04:59,220
Free?

113
00:05:01,060 --> 00:05:02,099
People like us

114
00:05:02,100 --> 00:05:03,974
are bound hand and foot
by resentment and hatred,

115
00:05:03,975 --> 00:05:05,179
clinging to our very bones,

116
00:05:05,180 --> 00:05:06,620
with no release.

117
00:05:07,180 --> 00:05:08,980
We only live in misery.

118
00:05:12,220 --> 00:05:14,300
Do you like Chu Ying that much?

119
00:05:18,540 --> 00:05:20,179
Do you love her deeply,

120
00:05:20,180 --> 00:05:21,220
my sister-in-law?

121
00:05:24,700 --> 00:05:26,300
Just call her Princess.

122
00:05:26,380 --> 00:05:28,220
Do not address her as family.

123
00:05:29,020 --> 00:05:30,140
And besides,

124
00:05:32,420 --> 00:05:35,020
I will sever all ties with her soon.

125
00:05:36,180 --> 00:05:38,740
Do you truly believe what you just said?

126
00:05:41,100 --> 00:05:43,000
If the Grand Princess
were to march with you,

127
00:05:43,660 --> 00:05:44,779
would you really be able...

128
00:05:44,780 --> 00:05:45,979
There is no if.

129
00:05:45,980 --> 00:05:48,300
She has already decided not to go.

130
00:05:49,740 --> 00:05:51,700
That does not suit her nature.

131
00:05:52,900 --> 00:05:54,860
I find it strange as well.

132
00:05:57,340 --> 00:05:58,900
But perhaps it is for the best.

133
00:06:03,180 --> 00:06:04,259
If there is no revenge,

134
00:06:04,260 --> 00:06:07,220
Uncle and you
will never escape this torment.

135
00:06:07,312 --> 00:06:08,432
If there is revenge,

136
00:06:08,700 --> 00:06:11,300
you and I will lose
the ones we love most.

137
00:06:12,740 --> 00:06:14,219
The battlefield is merciless.

138
00:06:14,220 --> 00:06:15,939
It may well be a road of no return,

139
00:06:15,940 --> 00:06:17,460
with both sides destroyed.

140
00:06:18,900 --> 00:06:20,300
Since that is so,

141
00:06:20,940 --> 00:06:23,020
I urge you to pull back from the brink,

142
00:06:23,820 --> 00:06:25,300
and turn back while you still can.

143
00:06:26,900 --> 00:06:28,340
Things have come this far.

144
00:06:29,180 --> 00:06:31,220
There is no turning back now.

145
00:06:31,980 --> 00:06:34,780
Just say no more.

146
00:06:50,060 --> 00:06:51,219
By the end of this month,

147
00:06:51,220 --> 00:06:53,619
you will be three months pregnant.

148
00:06:53,620 --> 00:06:55,540
Why don't you look pregnant at all?

149
00:06:55,820 --> 00:06:59,740
Perhaps this child is born different.

150
00:07:01,420 --> 00:07:03,140
Then you do not plan to tell him?

151
00:07:05,820 --> 00:07:07,620
I must not unsettle his morale.

152
00:07:08,980 --> 00:07:10,340
People are strange.

153
00:07:11,140 --> 00:07:12,900
Once they have something to hold on to,

154
00:07:13,020 --> 00:07:14,859
they grow softer toward the world,

155
00:07:14,860 --> 00:07:17,060
without even realizing it.

156
00:07:22,020 --> 00:07:25,500
I want Sun Gong to show
no softness at all,

157
00:07:26,180 --> 00:07:28,620
to wield the dragon-patterned sword
of the Chu clan,

158
00:07:29,700 --> 00:07:32,019
and cut down
every enemy at the frontier.

159
00:07:32,020 --> 00:07:34,100
And if there are
no enemies at the frontier,

160
00:07:35,820 --> 00:07:38,460
can you face that cruel truth?

161
00:07:39,900 --> 00:07:42,620
Our recent investigations
found nothing amiss.

162
00:07:43,620 --> 00:07:45,820
I only hope he lives up
to your devotion.

163
00:07:47,500 --> 00:07:49,620
I can feel that he loves me.

164
00:07:52,460 --> 00:07:55,820
That is why I choose
to give him one more chance.

165
00:08:31,820 --> 00:08:32,939
Your Majesty.

166
00:08:32,940 --> 00:08:33,459
I,

167
00:08:33,460 --> 00:08:34,859
heir to the Duke of Ying,

168
00:08:34,860 --> 00:08:37,780
former sixth-rank commander
of the Eastern City Garrison,

169
00:08:37,780 --> 00:08:40,459
now a fourth-rank blade-bearing guard
at Your Majesty's side, Duanmu Zhi,

170
00:08:40,460 --> 00:08:41,820
request to lead the campaign.

171
00:08:41,860 --> 00:08:44,019
I am willing to go to the frontier
in Your Majesty's stead,

172
00:08:44,020 --> 00:08:44,899
defeat the enemy,

173
00:08:44,900 --> 00:08:46,259
and defend our realm.

174
00:08:46,260 --> 00:08:47,380
Very well.

175
00:08:50,020 --> 00:08:51,140
I grant it.

176
00:08:52,740 --> 00:08:53,939
Frankly,

177
00:08:53,940 --> 00:08:55,019
Duanmu Zhi

178
00:08:55,020 --> 00:08:57,700
is better suited than I am
to command an army.

179
00:08:58,100 --> 00:08:59,979
A fine sword belongs with a true hero.

180
00:08:59,980 --> 00:09:00,940
Come.

181
00:09:01,300 --> 00:09:03,940
I bestow my Youlong Sword upon you.

182
00:09:04,540 --> 00:09:05,740
Thank you, Your Majesty.

183
00:09:06,320 --> 00:09:08,979
Your Majesty. Changing commanders
on the eve of battle is a grave risk.

184
00:09:08,980 --> 00:09:09,699
And the soldiers...

185
00:09:09,700 --> 00:09:11,659
If the soldiers can look to General Duanmu

186
00:09:11,660 --> 00:09:13,739
as the very image
of a Great Qian warrior,

187
00:09:13,740 --> 00:09:15,779
then on the battlefield

188
00:09:15,780 --> 00:09:17,179
our forces will be unstoppable,

189
00:09:17,180 --> 00:09:18,620
and never know defeat.

190
00:09:20,300 --> 00:09:21,420
Duanmu Zhi.

191
00:09:23,140 --> 00:09:23,859
Here.

192
00:09:23,860 --> 00:09:26,739
I now appoint you
Commander of the Banner Guards,

193
00:09:26,740 --> 00:09:28,779
to lead the imperial campaign
in my stead

194
00:09:28,780 --> 00:09:30,019
and defend the realm.

195
00:09:30,020 --> 00:09:31,140
Yes.

196
00:09:31,260 --> 00:09:32,979
Your Majesty, you must not.

197
00:09:32,980 --> 00:09:35,179
The entire army already knows
you would lead in person.

198
00:09:35,180 --> 00:09:36,059
If you withdraw now,

199
00:09:36,060 --> 00:09:37,779
morale will collapse.

200
00:09:37,780 --> 00:09:40,699
Yes, Your Majesty.
This is your first time

201
00:09:40,700 --> 00:09:42,420
establishing authority in the army.

202
00:09:42,740 --> 00:09:44,499
If you withdraw at the last moment,

203
00:09:44,500 --> 00:09:46,340
wouldn't that make a mockery of it?

204
00:09:47,580 --> 00:09:48,700
A mockery?

205
00:09:48,860 --> 00:09:50,620
When have I not been a mockery?

206
00:09:50,700 --> 00:09:51,859
When I danced in the palace,

207
00:09:51,860 --> 00:09:53,699
was that not a mockery to you?

208
00:09:53,700 --> 00:09:56,220
When I built Yanbo Parlor,
was that not a mockery?

209
00:09:59,500 --> 00:10:00,939
You all see me

210
00:10:00,940 --> 00:10:03,340
as nothing but an emperor who dances.

211
00:10:04,900 --> 00:10:06,540
Then let it be a mockery.

212
00:10:09,580 --> 00:10:11,980
Since His Majesty has decided,

213
00:10:12,180 --> 00:10:13,779
we respectfully send off General Duanmu

214
00:10:13,780 --> 00:10:16,820
and General Sun to the battlefield.

215
00:10:17,420 --> 00:10:20,500
May all our generals return in triumph.

216
00:10:20,820 --> 00:10:24,300
May all our generals return in triumph.

217
00:11:12,420 --> 00:11:14,360
(Five months later)
Signals arrive from the frontier.

218
00:11:14,360 --> 00:11:15,499
The time has come.

219
00:11:15,500 --> 00:11:16,620
Move.

220
00:11:33,820 --> 00:11:34,859
Reporting, Eunuch.

221
00:11:34,860 --> 00:11:37,219
Our men outside the palace
have taken control of the Capital.

222
00:11:37,220 --> 00:11:38,219
The palace guards inside

223
00:11:38,220 --> 00:11:40,260
have been nearly wiped out.

224
00:11:41,100 --> 00:11:43,459
As expected of elite troops.

225
00:11:43,460 --> 00:11:46,540
But the Grand Princess
is nowhere to be found.

226
00:11:49,420 --> 00:11:50,539
Search.

227
00:11:50,540 --> 00:11:51,779
Search the entire palace.

228
00:11:51,780 --> 00:11:53,340
Capture Chu Wuju alive.

229
00:11:54,140 --> 00:11:56,979
I will cut her and Chu Ying to pieces,

230
00:11:56,980 --> 00:11:59,059
to appease General Xiao's spirit.

231
00:11:59,060 --> 00:12:00,100
Yes.

232
00:12:05,860 --> 00:12:06,819
Assassins!

233
00:12:06,820 --> 00:12:08,180
Protect His Majesty!

234
00:12:15,220 --> 00:12:18,060
(I once had a dream.)

235
00:12:19,540 --> 00:12:23,140
(A dream that filled me with terror.)

236
00:13:02,980 --> 00:13:04,460
(Could it be today)

237
00:13:07,860 --> 00:13:10,740
(that dream comes true?)
